name: Totally Not Monday Mondays
descriptions: We meet up at 9am to give away free energy drinks to the first 30 people to show up. There are also contests to enter to win prizes.

name: Search and Recruit Wednesdays
descriptions: We host booths in different areas to promote the club. We give people tickets to enter raffles for our club.

name: Caffeinated Fridays
descriptions: We host parties at our main venues. We have games, bars, free commercial Wifi and seating for our members to socialize and connect.
